<title>qlby byk frḥạn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- qlby byk frḥạn qlby byk sẖbʿạn ạhtf wạ̉rnm lyk wạ̉dws ʿly̱ ạlạ̉ḥzạn
 1- tyjy tjạrb ạ̉w ḥrwb mn kl jạnb ạ̉ḥtmy̱ fy strk wạ̉gẖny lạ̉n wʿdk ʿny tḥạrb
 2- ḥbk ykfy ạ̹nh ymḥy kl ḍfʿy lw ḥyạty ạ̉qḍyhạ ạ̉sẖkr ʿmr mạ ʿmry ywfy
 3- lyly̱ ạ̉gẖạny wạḥtfạl bạlly fdạny myn hạyfṣl ḥbh ʿny wwʿdh ạ̉bdạaⁿ lạ ynsạny</lyrics>
